skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: feelings log
des: Life happens and we go through chains of emotions every day. It's hard to keep track of mental health as we live our busy lives but Alexa can help! Simply tell Alexa how you feel and you'll be greeted with advice, quotes, and even songs to help you get through the day. Your feelings are logged each time for you to track and evaluate them later. Ask Alexa, "What were my feelings on (date/day)" or "Evaluate my recent feelings"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
